TabRuler 1.2

Ruler appears only when a field is selected.
Click on the ruler to create a tab.
Click and drag a tab mark to adjust it, move it down to clear it.
Grid option make tabs snap to choosen value.
Ruler copy/paste let you apply it to any number of fields.
When deselecting field, changes are automatically applied if Auto button is on.

